<title type="html"><![CDATA[2/27(Sat.)Taiwanese:slightly higher salary/Foxconn to roll out 3 electric vehicles by end of 2021(James)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=476&amp;p=498#p498"><![CDATA[
2/27(Sat.)Taiwan workers received slightly higher monthly salary in 2020/Taiwan’s Foxconn Group to roll out 3 electric vehicles by end of 2021(James Chang)<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">1st article:Taiwan workers received slightly higher monthly salary in 2020</span><br /><a href="http://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4132032" class="postlink">http://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4132032</a><br /><br />Discussion<br />(1) In your opinion, do you really feel your salary increase last year? Do you feel satisfied about your salary or your retire income?<br />(2)Do you know the difference between deflation and inflation?<br />(3)What can we do if we are unemployed? If you face this kind of situation, what will you do?<br />(4)Do you plan for your retirement? Please share to us.<br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">2nd article:Taiwan’s Foxconn Group to roll out 3 electric vehicles by end of 2021</span><br /><a href="http://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4132014" class="postlink">http://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4132014</a><br /><br />Discussion<br />(1)Do you feel Foxconn do the right thing to develop electric vehicles?<br />(2) Do you have the experience to drive or take a ride on electric vehicles?<br />(3)Tesla is one of the pioneer company in electric vehicle industry, do you know Elon Musk other plan for our world?<br />(4)If you had enough money, will you buy an electric vehicle for yourself?why?<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔！<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1000元 (學生:500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Mon Feb 22, 2021 12:51 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
